I think raptors are awesome!

* Iron Raptor kept the kitten safe in her arms as Prowl gave her a finaly 
hug and kiss before leaving for the shuttles, thinking of how he would do up 
there and sure that he could lead the Maximals to victory.
But there was no time to doddle and she quickly found herself moving towards 
the controle room and a speed where others would have to run to catch up to 
her.
She had recied Hysterias transmission and  slowed down as the doors to the 
comtrole room slid open, entering the room and seeing Hysteria with the 
blueprints to the ark on a console.
Iron Raptor approached her.*

" Got me those scans yet?"

* She didn't mean to be rude but she had to know what was going on up there, 
to make sure that the Maximals had the best advantage to victory.
Because she could see the whole ship from here and where enemy signatures 
were, they could see the signatures but would be traveling through the halls 
and unable to see too much beyond them.
And scanning and fighting could be very tricky if they tried it.*
